protection from sumitomo mitsui financial group, inc. see note18 to the consolidated financial statements for further information about such lending commitments.  additionally, we make investments accounted for under the equity method and we also make direct investments in real estate, both of which are included in other assets. direct investments in
real estate are accounted for at cost less accumulated depreciation. see note13 to the consolidated financial statements for information about other assets.
