are not accounted for at fair value under the fair value option or at fair value in accordance with other u.s. gaap, their fair value is not included in the firms fair value hierarchy in notes6 through 8. had these borrowings been
included in the firms fair value hierarchy, substantially all would have been classified in level2 as of december2014 and december2013.
